headline: F5 Recognized as Leader in Web Application and API Protection (WAAP) in the KuppingerCole 2025 Leadership Compass Report
summary: SEATTLE, August 25, 2025--F5 (NASDAQ: FFIV), the global leader in delivering and securing every app and API, today announced that it has been recognized as an overall leader in the 2025 KuppingerCole Leadership Compass Report for Web Application and API Protection (WAAP) solutions. The report provides an overview of the WAAP market and assesses vendors based on innovation, market presence, and technology leadership.
